---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import img6 from '../assets/images/6.webp';
---

<section
    class="relative w-full bg-black py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden"
>
    <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center relative z-10"
    >
        <!-- Image Card -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative group order-2 lg:order-1">
            <div
                class="absolute -inset-4 bg-[#aba070]/15 blur-[100px] rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="relative rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-3xl transform transition-all duration-700 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:-rotate-1"
            >
                <Image
                    src={img6}
                    alt="Sesión de entrenamiento personal con Julián Restrepo"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[4/5] brightness-75 group-hover:brightness-100 transition-all duration-700"
                    loading="lazy"
                    decoding="async"
                    widths={[400, 600, 800]}
                    sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw"
                />
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent"
                >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Card -->
        <div
            class="w-full lg:w-1/2 p-10 md:p-14 rounded-[3rem] bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-3xl border border-white/10 shadow-3xl order-1 lg:order-2"
        >
            <h2
                class="text-[#aba070] font-black tracking-[0.4em] text-xs mb-6 uppercase italic"
            >
                BIENVENIDO
            </h2>

            <div
                class="space-y-8 text-gray-300 text-xl font-light leading-relaxed"
            >
                <p>
                    Si estás leyendo esto, probablemente ya intentaste hacerlo
                    por tu cuenta: rutinas copiadas, dietas sin sentido,
                    momentos de motivación que se desvanecen.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="text-white font-medium text-2xl tracking-tight leading-snug"
                >
                    Pero aquí no se trata de empezar una vez más, sino de <span
                        class="text-[#aba070] italic">empezar distinto</span
                    >.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Entrenar conmigo no es seguir un plan cualquiera; es
                    aprender a entender tu cuerpo, dominar tus hábitos y
                    encontrar una estructura que funcione para tu vida real.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Decorative Orb -->
    <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#aba070]/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full translate-x-1/4 translate-y-1/4"
    >
    </div>
</section>

